- The string array parameter `words` must not be null.
- The character array parameter `letters` must not be null.
- The integer array parameter `score` must not be null.
- The integer result is the maximum score of any valid set of words formed by using the given letters.
- Each letter in the character array parameter `letters` can only be used once.
- Each word in the string array parameter `words` cannot be used two or more times.
- The score of letters 'a', 'b', 'c', ..., 'z' is given by `score[0]`, `score[1]`, ..., `score[25]` respectively.